Package: cli-alert
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0)
Recommends: libnotify-bin, pulseaudio-utils
Suggests: espeak
Description: Terminal process completion notifier
 Sends OS-native desktop notifications and sounds when long-running
 terminal commands complete. Supports manual wrapping (alert <cmd>),
 automatic detection of commands exceeding a threshold, and Claude
 Code integration hooks. Cross-platform: macOS, Linux, WSL.
